2025-05-27 02:53:18,577 - INFO - 🧩 afterFlowable: style=FactStory, text='• 5. What type of music did Rozz Williams help pioneer? → Gothic rock' (page 76)
2025-05-27 02:53:18,577 - INFO - 🧩 afterFlowable: style=FactStory, text='• 6. How old was Doug Sahm when he could already play multiple instruments? → Under 10 years old' (page 76)
