2025-05-27 02:53:18,734 - INFO - 🧩 afterFlowable: style=Intro, text='Welcome to the amazing world of history, trivia, and delightfully random facts! This book is your guide to all the wild, weird, and wonderful things that happened around the world — and together, we’re about to answer the big question: What happened on November 6th? I’m TJ, a fact-lover from Saffron Walden. Whether this date is your birthday, your lizard’s, or just a lucky guess — this book’s for you. There are 119 facts packed into these pages. Let’s dive in! — TJ' (page 2)
